                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>next week. I should like<lb/> it much if it were possible to let me see a proof\n                before<lb/> you go to print. The same<lb/> morning I receive the proof<lb/> it shall\n                go back.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(6)\">Yours very respfy</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(7)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">M J Raphall</persName>\n            </p>\n            <div>\n                <p>\n                    <ref target=\"Occident_PDFs/Occ_17_22.pdf\">The above text refers to Occident\n                        Volume 17 No. 22 pages 128 through 129. Click here to view.</ref>\n                </p>\n            </div>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
